        <br><br>
        <strong>🎥 <a href="https://share.vidday.com/e/w-aht42f" style="color: var(--heather-light); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px;">share.vidday.com/e/w-aht42f</a></strong><br>
        <span style="font-size:12px; letter-spacing:0.08em; color: rgba(194,191,200,0.6);">PASSWORD: korbie2026</span>
